ForgeKit RPG Module — placeholder directory
============================================

This directory is reserved for the paid **ForgeKit RPG Module**. It is empty
on purpose so that the ForgeKit Core template starts without errors even when
the module is not installed.

To install the module:

1. Purchase ForgeKit RPG Module from one of the official stores:
   - itch.io:  https://forgekitstudio.itch.io/forgekit-rpg
   - Gumroad:  https://forgekitstudio.gumroad.com/l/forgekit-rpg
2. Download the distribution ZIP and unzip its contents directly into this
   directory (`addons/forgekit_rpg/`). After extraction you should see
   subdirectories such as `combat/`, `crafting/`, `inventory/`, `stats/`
   alongside `public_api.gd` and `module.manifest.tres`.
3. Activate your license by calling the MCP tool:
     `modules.activate_license("forgekit_rpg", "<your-license-key>")`
4. Restart the MCP server or call `project.reload` to unlock the RPG
   subsystems (Combat, Crafting, Inventory, Stats).

Do not delete this file. Git keeps empty directories only when at least one
tracked file lives inside them.
